<p>
    The remaining mystery of a studied protocol is that of what constitutes a valid session of messages. Or more
    specifically, what sequences of messages are valid during an exchange and what sequences aren&apos;t. This set of message
    sequences is best expressed by a finite state machine, specifically a Mealy machine

