    states, q0 &epsilon; Q is the initial state, &sum;I is a finite set of input symbols, &sum;O is a finite set of output symbols, &sigma; :
    Q x &sum;I &rarr; Q is the
    transition relation, and &lambda; : Qx&sum;I &rarr; &sum;O is the output relation.&quot;

